N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 16 ยง 255.173 - Compressor stations: ventilation

State Regulations

Each compressor station building must be ventilated to
ensure that employees are not endangered by the accumulation of gas in rooms, sumps, attics, pits, or other enclosed places. Notes
